summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical underground distribution easements over portions of Capitol Hill Addition to the City of Seattle, Division \#4; Schreiner's Garden Tracts; Black's Elliott Bay Addition to the City of Seattle; Maple Lead Addition to Green Lake Circle; Jordan's Acre Gardens; assessors plat of Normandy Park Highlands; John Buckley Donation Claim No. 42 in Section on 32, Township 24 North, Range 4 East and Lake Ballinger Garden Tracts.
